items.title: Awesome Jax
items.content_text: ### Libraries / New Libraries * [Mctx (⭐2.5k)](https://github.com/deepmind/mctx) - Monte Carlo tree search algorithms in native JAX. * [KFAC-JAX (⭐280)](https://github.com/deepmind/kfac-jax) - Second Order Optimization with Approximate Curvature for NNs. * [TF2JAX (⭐114)](https://github.com/deepmind/tf2jax) - Convert functions/graphs to JAX functions.
items.content_html:
Libraries / New Libraries

  • Mctx (⭐2.5k) - Monte Carlo tree search algorithms in native JAX.
  • KFAC-JAX (⭐280) - Second Order Optimization with Approximate Curvature for NNs.
  • TF2JAX (⭐114) - Convert functions/graphs to JAX functions.
